/#
   A type defining the cash settlement payment date(s) as either a set of explicit dates, together with applicable adjustments, or as a date relative to some other (anchor) date, or as any date in a range of contiguous business days.
 #/
record FpML5.confirmation.CashSettlementPaymentDate {
  # A series of dates that shall be subject to adjustment if they would otherwise fall on a day that is not a business day in the specified business centers, together with the convention for adjusting the date.
  adjustableDates : FpML5.confirmation.AdjustableDates

  # A date specified as some offset to another date (the anchor date).
  relativeDate : FpML5.confirmation.RelativeDateOffset

  # A range of contiguous business days.
  businessDateRange : FpML5.confirmation.BusinessDateRange

  id : string?

}

relativeDate.Name: relativeDate

businessDateRange.Name: businessDateRange
